body:
I'm getting sick of this thing that keeps popping up when I open the client. I haven't received any new key for a long time. There's no point in popping this thing into my eye when it's the same thing over and over and over again. Cmon, what's the point with this thing? You're not gaining anything by annoying people with this popup.

I disabled all notifications, so I'm pretty sure this is how it's supposed to be. Just make this like a small notification or remove it or make it optional. It serves no purpose for me, I have no intention to get into the hextech stuff any time soon. I just want to play some games for fun.

Remove the popup! {{champion:202}}
